flowchart LR
    User([👤 Customer<br/>uploads photo + text])
    User --> Upload[POST /api/upload-image<br/>multipart, ≤5MB, auto-resize 1024px]
    Upload --> Claim[POST /api/claim]

    Claim --> Orchestrator{🎼 Orchestrator}

    Orchestrator --> Intent[🎯 IntentAgent<br/>gemini-2.5-flash<br/>+ function calling]
    Intent --> Damage[📸 DamageAgent<br/>gemini-2.5-flash Vision<br/>+ structured output]
    Damage --> Comp[💰 CompensationAgent<br/>gemini-2.5-flash<br/>+ RAG policy lookup]
    Comp --> Verify[✅ VerifierAgent<br/>hard-cap checks<br/>+ tone review]

    Verify -->|approve| Final[Final Offer]
    Verify -->|revise| Comp
    Verify -->|escalate| Human[🚨 Human Queue]

    subgraph Data
        Policies[(📋 policies.json<br/>10 rules)]
        KB[(📚 knowledge_base.json<br/>30 entries)]
    end
    Comp -.uses.-> Policies
    Damage -.uses.-> KB

    Final --> WS[WebSocket /ws<br/>streams agent_trace events]
    WS --> UI[💻 Web UI<br/>Damage Card / Offer Card / Live Trace]

    style Intent fill:#4f46e5,color:#fff
    style Damage fill:#f59e0b,color:#fff
    style Comp fill:#10b981,color:#fff
    style Verify fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style Human fill:#ef4444,color:#fff
    style Orchestrator fill:#7c3aed,color:#fff
